quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  4,15,"∆Āen wa…óoo…ďe paŇčkare jeenugol e rew…ďe mon …ďen, woni laa…ďu…ďe maa ko woori …óum, seedinee e ma…ď…ďe wor…ďe nayo juul…ďe nun…óu…ďe. Si …ďen seedike yi'ugol rew…ďe …ďen no faggitoo paŇčkare …óen, haray wa…óiree leptugol …ďe ngol jogitagol ngol ka cuu…ói haa maayde nden arana …ďe, maa Alla Wa…óana …ďe laawol yawtirngol ko wanaa jogiteede nden ka cuu…ói. Refti Alla ∆Āanngini yaltirngal ma…ď…ďe ngal …ďaawo …óum, O Sar'ini piyugol jiwo jeenu…óo mo jombaaka on sawru teemedere e ra…óeede hitaande, rajmeede ware debbo jinu…óo jommbaa…óo on."
  4,16,"∆Āen wor…ďe …ói…óo faggitii…ďe paŇčkare jinaa …óen, woni ko res…ďe maa ko wonaa …óum, leptiree…ďe …óemngal e junngo hoyniron …ďe …óum. Si …ďe yiltike e on bone mo mo∆ī∆īini golle ma…ď…ďe, haray …óuurnee e lorrugol …ďe ; sabu tuuu…óo e junuubi no wa'i wa on mo faggitaaki …óum. Pellet, Alla Laatike Ja…ďoowo tuubuubuyee jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen Hinnotoo…óo …ďe. Yonndinorgol ngol leptugol …óon tun, ko aranun Farlanoo, refti …óum Momtiraa piyugol mo jommbaa maa mo jommbaaka on ra…óoo mo, woppa wara jom…ďu…óo maa jommbaa."
  4,17,"Anndee ko Alla Ja…ďanta tuubuubuyee, ko …ďen faggitoray…ďe goopi e geddi e dow majjere ma…ď…ďe bone …óin geddi ; ko wano non kadi kala faggitor…óo goopi foti o tewi maa o tewaaki, hooti …ďe ruttiie Joomi ma…ď…ďe ado maayde nden ; …ďen …óon, Alla Ja…ďanay …ďe tuubuubuyee, O Yawtana …ďe goopi ma…ď…ďe. Alla Laatike Anndu…óo fiyakuuji tagu Makko ngun, √Ďee√Īu…óo e Toppitagol Makko ngol Sar'ina."
  4,18,"Alla Ja…ďataa tuubuubuyee …ďen duumotoo…ďe e geddi …ďe roŇčka tuubude e majji haa …óe…ó…óere maayde nannga …ďe, ontuma gooto e ma…ď…ďe wi'a : "Min mi tuubii jooni e ko mi faggitii kon e geddi. Alla Ja…ďataa fahin, tuubuubuyee …ďen maayidoo…ďe e keeferaaku. ∆Āen yeddoo…ďe duumo- too…ďe e geddi …óon, e …ďen maayidoo…ďe e keeferaaku, Men Hebilanii …ďe fow lepte muusu…óe."
  4,19,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe Alla e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen, dagaŇčtaako on nde ronirton rew…ďe baabiraa…ďe mon e …ďadii…ďe mon wano jawdi ronirtee, maa etagol no resira…ďe maa no resinira …ďe on mo faala…óon maa ha…óon …ďe reseede. DagaŇčtaako on kadi jogitorgol resaa…ďe mon …ďen …ďe a√Īu…óon fii no lorriron …ďe haa …ďe jonnita on yoga e kon ko okkuno…óon …ďe e teŇče maa ko nanndi heen si wanaa hara …ďe faggiti paŇčkare …ďanngu…óo wano jinugol ; si …ďe huuwii …óum, ina dagano on jogitorgol …ďe e …ďi…ótinana …ďe fii no …ďe soktitora kon ko okkuno…óon …ďe. Wonndiree e rew…ďe mon …ďen no mo∆ī∆īiri, accon lorrugol …ďe, …óu…ó…óinon mo∆ī∆īagol e ma…ď…ďe. Si on a√Īirii…ďe fiyaake aduna, mu√Ī√Īee ; sabu no jortaa nde Alla Wa…óata e kon ko a√Īu…óon mo∆ī∆īere …óuu…óunde aduna e laakara."